<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الْمَأْذُونِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الْإِذْنُ:</span> الْإِعْلَامُ لُغَةً<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إيرَادُ كِتَابِ الْمَأْذُونِ بَعْدَ كِتَابِ الْحَجْرِ ظَاهِرُ الْمُنَاسَبَةِ، إذْ الْإِذْنُ يَقْتَضِي سَبْقَ الْحَجْرِ (وَهُوَ فِي اللُّغَةِ عِبَارَةٌ عَنْ الْإِعْلَامِ،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>